<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a24 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .credentials {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff6b6b;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üîí Password Reset</h1>
        <p>Your Password Has Been Reset</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Your password has been reset by the system administrator. You can now log in using the new temporary password below.</p>
        
        <div class="credentials">
            <h3>üîê Your New Login Credentials</h3>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
            <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <code>{{temporaryPassword}}</code></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Notice:</strong><br>
            For your security, you must change your password on your first login. The temporary password above will only work once.
        </div>
        
        <p>Click the button below to access your account:</p>
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login to Your Account</a>
        
        <p><strong>If you did not request this password reset, please contact our support team immediately at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</strong></p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        <strong>School Management System Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} School Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
